metadata.name: Pamiee - Decora Girl
metadata.description:
Pamiee himself with Decora Style
This bring back so much memories of my friend that passed away last year, she lost at the age of 19 in 2021. She loves Lolita & Decora, we usually dress as Decora girl at the cosplay convention together. I usually borrow the accessories from her. There was a fight between us and we stop talking to each other for 3 years,  then what happen is my friend told me that she just passed away. But during the pandemic, no one can make it to visit her funeral. I tried my best to sneak out to visit her funeral, It was sad,  the funeral was cold because there are no one there visit her due to Covid. But i think that she would be happy knowing that i came to her funeral.
Canvas size: 2000*2500
